independent expert on the situation of human rights in Burundi. 
</p>
<p>61. During the ensuing discussion, at the same meeting, the following made statements: 
</p>
<p>                                                 
</p>
<p><b>6
</b>  Ibid. </p>

 <p> 
</p>
<p> (<i>a</i>) Representatives of States members of the Council: Canada, Egypt (on behalf 
