</p>
<p>62. The representative of Egypt (on behalf of the Group of African States) made a second 
statement further explaining his position. 
</p>
<p>63. At the same meeting, the Minister of National Solidarity, Human Rights and Gender of 
Burundi made concluding remarks. 
